androidx.recyclerview.widget

Interface ListUpdateCallback

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdapterListUpdateCallback, BatchingListUpdateCallback, SortedList.BatchedCallback, SortedList.Callback, SortedListAdapterCallback

    public interface ListUpdateCallback
    An interface that can receive Update operations that are applied to a list.

    This class can be used together with DiffUtil to detect changes between two lists.
